This package uses quilt to manage all modifications. See

  /usr/share/doc/quilt/quilt.pdf.gz

to get more information on how to use it.

To apply and unapply all patches, you can run:

 quilt push -a
 quilt pop -a

ensuring that you have set QUILT_PATCHES=debian/patches, or alternatively

 debian/rules patch
 debian/rules unpatch

